WEBVTT

00:01:55.880 --> 00:02:00.703
Yuqori darajadagi kortizol 
neyronlar orasidagi

00:02:00.703 --> 00:02:03.267
sinaptik bog’lanishlarning yo’qolishiga

00:02:03.267 --> 00:02:06.871
va miyaning diqqat, qaror, 
hukm chiqarish va ijtimoiy aloqa xulqini

00:02:06.871 --> 00:02:08.253
tartibga soluvchi soha,

00:02:08.253 --> 00:02:09.379
prefrontal qobiqning

00:02:09.379 --> 00:02:11.620
kichrayishiga olib keladi.

00:02:11.620 --> 00:02:16.437
U gippokamda yangi 
miya hujayralari yaralishini

00:02:16.437 --> 00:02:19.925
kamaytiradi. Surunkali stress narsalarni

00:02:19.925 --> 00:02:21.401
o'rganish va eslab qolishni

00:02:21.401 --> 00:02:24.324
qiyinlashtiradi, oqibatda jiddiy ruhiy

00:02:24.324 --> 00:02:28.875
hastalik-depressiya, 
alsgeymer kasalligiga sharoit yaratadi.

00:02:28.875 --> 00:02:33.181
Stress oqibati miyaning DNK qatlamigacha
kirib boradi.